snippet.title: Godzilla x Kong : The New Empire | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Witness the rise of a new empire. #GodzillaXKong - Only in theaters 2024

The epic battle continues! We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: CID cast Shivaji Satam, Aditya Srivastava at crematorium for last rites of late actor Dinesh Phadnis
snippet.description:
CID cast members Shivaji Satam, Aditya Srivastava, Tanya Abrol, and Ansha Sayed gathered at the crematorium to pay their respects to the late actor Dinesh Phadnis, who passed away last night. His last rites took place at Daulat Nagar crematorium in Borivali around 10:30-11 am. The actor, who battled for his life, succumbed around 12 am after being admitted to Tunga Hospital in Mumbai. ETimes TV got to speak with the actors, who shared their fond memories.

snippet.title: Bobby Deol Interview | ‚ÄòAlways knew Animal will work‚Äô | Ranbir Kapoor | Gadar 2 | Dharmendra
snippet.description:
In a candid chat with Pinkvilla, Bobby Deol opens up about the historic success of Animal, the bond with Ranbir Kapoor on the sets, and the vision of director Sandeep Reddy Vanga. The actor decodes his iconic entry scene and speaks from his heart about the success tasted by brother Sunny Deol and father Dharmendra in 2023 with Gadar 2 and Rocky Aur Rani Kii Prem Kahaani. Bobby also gives an update on Soldier 2, Animal 2 and Apne 2 and explains what would it take for him to come on board a comedy. Watch Video.
